Is Linna Noir a real influencer — or is she completely AI-generated? 

@linnanoir, the Instagram influencer who has taken the internet by storm with nearly 100K followers and millions of video views. The debate is real: some people swear she's human, while others are convinced she's an AI-generated persona built to fool the algorithm.
We analyzed her photos, her videos, her engagement, and her overall online presence — and what we found will surprise you.
